{"id":295889,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/05/维权网-杭州数百名访民请愿被清场，多人被抓（/","date":"2013-05-29T17:31:00Z","modified":"2013-05-29T17:31:00Z","title":"维权网 | 杭州数百名访民请愿被清场，多人被抓（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员潘高锋报道）多年来，杭州访民每个星期三都到市政府门前集会请愿，尽管每次都被警察驱散，但他们从不退缩，风雨无阻，这已成惯例。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>然而，今天（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">29</span><span>日</span><span>）的情况与以往不同。上午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>点左右，当访民们从四面八方赶来时，市政府门前已布满警察和便衣，不准访民靠近，并将他们驱赶到附近的万向公园。浙江民主党人王富华是杭州木材厂职工，他带领该厂职工维权已有近十年历史，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2005</span><span>年曾因集体维权被拘留七天，后又将公安告上法庭。今天上午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>点，他和本厂退休工人应志温等数十人来到市政府，结果被警察驱逐到万向公园。他看到警察在驱赶访民的过程中对访民动粗，便上前指责，结果被拉上警车送拱墅区巡特警大队关押起来。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">77</span><span>岁的应志温看到王富华被抓便上前与警察论理，结果也被抓到拱墅区巡特警大队。杭州著名维权人士朱瑛娣、梁丽婉随后也被抓到拱墅区巡特警大队关押。除王富华、应志温、朱瑛娣、梁丽婉外，还有杨幸华、徐彩英、殷小翠、郭文娟等六、七人也被关到拱朝墅区巡特警大队。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">77</span><span>岁的应志温因身体不好吃不下巡特警大队的饭，在中午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>点半由王富华陪同出来。而朱瑛娣、梁丽婉等人则被关到下午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>点多才放出来。警察要朱、梁等人做笔录，但她们拒绝回答任何问题，说自己没有任何违法行为，而警察滥抓无辜则是严重的违法行为，应当追究法律责任。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>据访民估计，今天被驱逐的访民大约有数百人，而着装的警察也有上百人。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-uLh4VcN_Hog/UaYwFu5vZrI/AAAAAAAAiq0/gigLNj3pnP0/s1600/1628.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-uLh4VcN_Hog/UaYwFu5vZrI/AAAAAAAAiq0/gigLNj3pnP0/s320/1628.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-1NsR-0AvGAI/UaYwE8-wZJI/AAAAAAAAiqs/QfCxyhzA-q0/s1600/100_1629.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-1NsR-0AvGAI/UaYwE8-wZJI/AAAAAAAAiqs/QfCxyhzA-q0/s320/100_1629.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-K2iLRxXLruc/UaYwKfofKbI/AAAAAAAAirE/CpyAj2CQjZ4/s1600/101657_%25E5%2589%25AF%25E6%259C%25AC.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-K2iLRxXLruc/UaYwKfofKbI/AAAAAAAAirE/CpyAj2CQjZ4/s1600/101657_%25E5%2589%25AF%25E6%259C%25AC.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-t14dYHNqHkI/UaYwNW_4EGI/AAAAAAAAirM/v8vR0HaFY88/s1600/20130529_144152__%25E5%2589%25AF%25E6%259C%25AC.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"182\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-t14dYHNqHkI/UaYwNW_4EGI/AAAAAAAAirM/v8vR0HaFY88/s1600/20130529_144152__%25E5%2589%25AF%25E6%259C%25AC.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-2Tl9RvHMTmI/UaYwIQr52dI/AAAAAAAAiq8/4idA1jo1pKA/s1600/IMAG1752_%25E5%2589%25AF%25E6%259C%25AC.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"191\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-2Tl9RvHMTmI/UaYwIQr52dI/AAAAAAAAiq8/4idA1jo1pKA/s320/IMAG1752_%25E5%2589%25AF%25E6%259C%25AC.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-9H6Vv4qgjWk/UaYwOYC9YWI/AAAAAAAAirc/pFaNJ2WJWno/s1600/IMAG1760.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"288\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-9H6Vv4qgjWk/UaYwOYC9YWI/AAAAAAAAirc/pFaNJ2WJWno/s320/IMAG1760.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-xJ6DQcPyRiI/UaYwNcc8X8I/AAAAAAAAirQ/-BD1BHe0_bE/s1600/IMAG1766.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"191\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-xJ6DQcPyRiI/UaYwNcc8X8I/AAAAAAAAirQ/-BD1BHe0_bE/s320/IMAG1766.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-OwQRlsfOTXU/UaYwSHByiEI/A